] AS [tableid],[currency].[versionnumber] AS [versionnumber],[currency].[createdon] AS [createdon],[currency].[modifiedon] AS [modifiedon],[currency].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete],[currency].[PartitionId] COLLATE Latin1_General_100_CI_AS_KS_WS_SC_UTF8 AS [PartitionId],CASE [currency].[iseuro] WHEN 0 THEN 'No'  WHEN 1 THEN 'Yes'  END AS iseuro_$label,CASE [currency].[ltmroundofftypelineamount] WHEN 0 THEN 'Ordinary'  WHEN 1 THEN 'RoundDown'  WHEN 2 THEN 'RoundUp'  END AS ltmroundofftypelineamount_$label,CASE [currency].[roundofftypeassetdep_jp] WHEN 0 THEN 'Ordinary'  WHEN 1 THEN 'RoundDown'  WHEN 2 THEN 'RoundUp'  END AS roundofftypeassetdep_jp_$label,CASE [currency].[roundofftypeprice] WHEN 0 THEN 'Ordinary'  WHEN 1 THEN 'RoundDown'  WHEN 2 THEN 'RoundUp'  END AS roundofftypeprice_$label,CASE [currency].[roundofftypepurch] WHEN 0 THEN 'Ordinary'  WHEN 1 THEN 'RoundDown'  WHEN 2 THEN 'RoundUp'  END AS roundofftypepurch_$label,CASE [currency].[roundofftypesales] WHEN 0 THEN 'Ordinary'  WHEN 1 THEN 'RoundDown'  WHEN 2 THEN 'RoundUp'  END AS roundofftypesales_$label
